item.title: I need HELP!
item.dc:creator: @Bromann Bromann
item.description:
@Bromann wrote:

Your client needs to be set to localhost (127.0.0.1) while the server is running.

To run the server find the run.bat in the server files.

Once its running you just open up the client that is set to 127.0.0.1 (this is usually defined in client.java in the client source folder, though some clients have a built-in IP/port field) you can log in and test your work.
